# ─── Resend (email delivery) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Sign up free at https://resend.com
# 2. Go to API Keys → Create API Key
# 3. Paste the key below
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# • Without a verified domain, Resend only allows sending FROM onboarding@resend.dev
#   and only TO your own verified email address (fine for testing).
# • To send FROM hello@staplerlabs.com:
#   1. Go to Resend → Domains → Add Domain → staplerlabs.com
#   2. Add the DNS TXT/MX records they give you
#   3. Change the `from` address in src/app/api/contact/route.ts
